    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You know how to get the full damage out of a weapon type your class doesnâ€™t normally use.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Character level 3rd, proficiency with selected weapon type.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: Choose one weapon type (small arms, longarms, heavy weapons, etc.). You gain specialization in that weapon type, which means you add your character level to damage with the selected weapon type, or half your character level for small arms or operative melee weapons. You can never have specialization in grenades.</span></p>",
